{"title":"七律：有所思","date":"1966-6-0","authors":[],"contents":[{"text":"七律：有所思  ［毛泽东］","type":"title"},{"text":"有所思","type":"subtitle"},{"text":"毛泽东","type":"subtitle"},{"text":"1966.06.00","type":"subtitle"},{"text":"正是神都有事时，","type":"subtitle"},{"text":"又来南国踏芳枝。","type":"subtitle"},{"text":"青松怒向苍天发，","type":"subtitle"},{"text":"败叶纷随碧水驰。","type":"subtitle"},{"text":"一阵风雷惊世界，","type":"subtitle"},{"text":"满街红绿走旌旗。","type":"subtitle"},{"text":"凭阑静听潇潇雨，","type":"subtitle"},{"text":"故国人民有所思。","type":"subtitle"}]}